  </table>

  <p>The math is simple: points = rake paid * XX%. So, for example, if you paid 10 chips in rake and you sit in position #1 and there are 7+ players,
  you will get 12 points - yes, more than you paid in rake! You will be able to exchange points to chips at My Account page 
  once you reach 100 points.</p>

  <p>This is a rough initial implementation of the reward system. We are constantly looking into enhancing the game, so please check it out often. 
  Also if you have any questions or suggestions - do not hesitate to contact us.</p>

</div>